response.overview: Denise Ho looks forward with MEMENTO 2013, a significant concert that celebrates her memories. Having been out and about in Taiwan alone the last four years, Denise returns to Hong Kong a stronger and more well-rounded artist and lets her glamour come through in full in her third concert at the Hong Kong Coliseum held in October 2013.
response.title: HOCC MEMENTO 2013 Concert
